One mother, who asked not to be named, said: ‘It was only by chance that I happened to notice it on the computer after my daughter had used it.

'He had sent it to everyone in her form. Apparently it was taken in a fun photo booth at a school fete on Monday but why was he emailing it to the children?

‘It’s very inappropriate. We’ve got a possible serial killer in Colchester.’

